Key Match Events: C. Gakpo scored the equalizing goal for the Netherlands at 47 minutes
M. Depay scored the go-ahead goal for the Netherlands at 75 minutes
M. Sabitzer scored the winning goal for Austria at 80 minutes
Post-Match Reflections: Marcel Sabitzer was named Player of the Match
Miscellaneous Highlights: Austria topped Group D and will face the runners-up in Group F in the last 16
The Netherlands could face England in the last 16 if they finish as one of the best four third-place teams
Others: The match was played in Berlin
The Netherlands had 0.95 xG compared to Austria's 1.73
